{"tid":1945822,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港獨立學社 《本土與獨立》","createTime":"2020-03-27T09:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T07:32:32.000Z","uid":173326,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47a2b38c7313f573d139e320ca5d230a3921ce71","tid":1945822,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"《本土與獨立》<br />\n<br />\n自本土思潮興起，出現了不少政治人物自居本土，打著「香港優先」的旗號，獲得不少民眾支持。但事實上，你又真的知道甚麼是「本土派」嗎？而「獨立派」又與「本土派」之間有著甚麼關係？<br />\n<br />\n簡而言之，本土是一條問題，而獨立就是解答這條問題的答案之一。<br />\n<br />\n本土與泛民不同的地方在於，本土希望保留永久的中港區隔，比起泛民「大愛式」的包容所有香港人，本土派更會區分他者與我者，以保障「真。香港人」的利益。就例如我們耳熟能詳的收回單程證審批權、取消普教中、新移民福利政策等等。而為了捍衛本土，必然的是抗衡赤化的加速。這些都是「本土派」美好的願景。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，我們又可以如何達到這些願景呢？<br />\n<br />\n於是，就有著「獨立派」的出現。「香港獨立」就是達到「本土願景」最直接的做法。只要香港能永久與中國（不論甚麼政權當權）切割，我們就有著實現「本土優先」的權利，也能自己掌控所有政策，以充分保障香港人的利益。<br />\n<br />\n當然，也有不少本土派不主張「獨立」這條出路，他們認為比起永久切割這種難度較高，較一刀切的做法，仍然有著其他更簡單的做法以保障本土利益。但從邏輯上而言，本土派可以「不主張」獨立，但也不應該「反對」我們有獨立的權利。故此，「前途自決」就成為大部分本土派的共通點。「獨立派」就是「本土派」的其中一份子。大家目標一致，不強求中共倒台，只求保障港人。只是「獨立派」希望用更直接的做法達到願景，大家在手段上各有不同罷了。<br />\n<br />\n九月立法會選舉將至，不少候選人也高舉「本土」旗號，企圖博取民眾支持。支持進攻選舉又希望投票給本土素人的朋友，謹記細閱眾候選人的政綱，分清楚究竟他是「泛民」、「本土」甚或「激進本土」，投選出自己心目中最理想的代議士。<br />\n<br />\n有關議會戰線，我們未來會另作文宣分析～有意見的朋友也歡迎留言向我們提議未來文宣的主題！我們也會樂意聽取🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n #本土與獨立<br />\n#香港獨立唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUMkVLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUMkVLn.jpg&h=5cb21790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFPiHqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFPiHqq.jpg&h=710f54e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ba5mFcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBa5mFcb.jpg&h=55427334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSuiHqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSuiHqz.jpg&h=4f67718c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjQmFci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjQmFci.jpg&h=3f085aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hKdjrSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhKdjrSm.jpg&h=dbdc0f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsauce:<br />\nIg: @hk_independence_institute<br />\ntg: @hk_independence_institute<br />\nfb:香港獨立學社"},{"pid":"1f8a1308567bb625b5beb4344e02ba947cb912b6","tid":1945822,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"記得留意埋香港民族陣綫<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHK.NationFront&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=dfcda81a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront</a>"},{"pid":"4da0e716f4cd62761cfe77b9420bc1dd7a505d93","tid":1945822,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"正經POST 推"},{"pid":"377a4901434e1bd4bd8fc7e3187470ca133e64fb","tid":1945822,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b18a4e1fdb0685c893e4f4752c978179fd9b4cbc","tid":1945822,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-hong-kong-independence&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=93b25da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence</a>"},{"pid":"1c947e0e44a2397f56bf569d01ebe33a225f4537","tid":1945822,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"仲以為有書買"},{"pid":"61a4d7ef73dda8d445a2571241d3c509876d6e49","tid":1945822,"uid":1