etition/us-nominate-dr-shih-c-chen-taiwan-doh-minister-new-chair-who</a>"},{"pid":"0fb32969b533540505844b78397f7bd2b1b4782c","tid":1945822,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"66b94ca9eab8c421c15af066d7e78820e8b05a4c","tid":1945822,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"幾好 唔該樓主 出色"},{"pid":"86fb82dcf0487a2c095ba0b6103fc5b1f5780a9b","tid":1945822,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5833a8d3bc9a1c7a61c3e24dbb9d5dfe3b1c0998","tid":1945822,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951e3086eb2e1290b8c68c23e793e0435a264e7f","tid":1945822,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n每個人都要睇"},{"pid":"b7a302d281df292591b753e160f77474189232b2","tid":1945822,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56216c35aaa16eabe695463b34d5ac16c010aca4","tid":1945822,"uid":311663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKZiJge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKZiJge.jpg&h=1ddb5aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【毋忘八三一憤怒 毋忘三三一初衷| 在艱彌厲 戰鬥到底】<br />\n<br />\n下週二，831太子恐襲事件七個月，同時亦是香港首場反修例全民大遊行一週年，其後在6月9號全面爆發反送中抗爭，一年過去抗爭仍然繼續持續，雖不容置疑的是街頭抗爭稍有冷卻，但我等相信香港民族的反抗意志絕不會磨滅。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘八三一憤怒，毋忘三三一初衷，悼念逝去的戰友要的不是鮮花蠟燭，完成戰友們的遺願就是最好的悼念方法！<br />\n<br />\n3月31號，懇請香港民族用盡一切辦法，讓泯滅人性者負上應有代價，在艱彌厲戰鬥到底！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港&middot;時代革命<br />\n香港獨立&middot;唯一出路"},{"pid":"ffb15c252ccb34db6350bc5553022d1bb842d9ee","tid":1945822,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951e3086eb2e1290b8c68c23e793e0435a264e7f","tid":1945822,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n每個人都要睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"兒登係垃圾<br />\n竟然無人理正經嘢"},{"pid":"70c808023d8fc9de5c6d17d54441bf0a00093187","tid":1945822,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08740cb409253e99338458f457c727aaecff575f","tid":1945822,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/QMfS1cr7/TP2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FQMfS1cr7%2FTP2.jpg&h=80cd68d9&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b18a4e1fdb0685c893e4f4752c978179fd9b4cbc","tid":1945822,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-hong-kong-independence&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=93b25da7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-hong-kong-independence</a>"}}